beer.beer_description:
PEACHARINE / RAKAU / SIMCOE

Here at Bracket we've been getting really into the stonefruit.

So with the recent addition of Peacharine to @freestylehops lineup we decided to get all of our fuzziest hops together for this juicy DIPA.

We couldn't be happier with the result. Pillowy mouthfeel, sweet but not too sweet and soft tropical and stone fruits. We would be lying if we said there wasn't a few similarities to Test Print here.
beer.beer_style: IPA - Imperial / Double New England / Hazy
